{{zh-hanzi|[[原]][[汁]]}}
=={{cmn}}==
From [[原]] original + [[汁]] juice

===Adjective===
{{cmn-adj|ts|pin=yuánzhī|pint=yuan2zhi1|rs=厂08}}

# the original essence of something; the authentic
# fresh; original

====Derived terms====
*[[原汁原味]] (fresh; no artificial flavors)
*[[原汁搞笑]] (fresh comedy)
*{{zh-ts|原汁蘆薈膠|原汁芦荟胶}} (fresh aloe juice gel)

===Noun===
{{cmn-noun|ts|pin=yuánzhī|pint=yuan2zhi1|rs=厂08}}

# the original juice that has been freshly squeezed from fruits or vegetables
# the original juice that results from cooking food; drippings

====Derived terms====
*{{zh-ts|蘆薈原汁|芦荟原汁}} (aloe juice)
*[[沙棘原汁]] ([[w:sea-buckthorn|sea-buckthorn]] juice)
*[[葡萄原汁]] (fresh-squeezed grape juice)

